headline: GM Is Fighting California on EVs. This Is What It Wants to Overturn and Why.
summary: General Motors  is an electric-vehicle advocate, but even it’s worried about California’s aggressive EV mandate.  Investors need to understand the mandate and why car companies are worried about one state’s policies.  The Wall Street Journal reported Sunday that GM was pushing to eliminate or modify California’s EV targets, citing a memo sent to employees.

headline: GM Is Pushing Hard to Tank California’s EV Mandate
summary: General Motors  went all in on electric cars.  Now it is racing to reverse the nation’s most aggressive EV mandate.  “We need your help!” GM said in an email it sent this past week to thousands of its white-collar employees.
